          <title>Brunson and Towns lead the Knicks past the Hawks 113-102 in Game 1 of their series</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Jalen Brunson scored 28 points, Karl-Anthony Towns had 19 of his 25 in the second half and the New York Knicks beat the Atlanta Hawks 113-102 in Game 1 of their Eastern Conference playoff series.]]></description>
